            "notes": "This deck focuses on using Brigid, Clachan's Heart as the commander to lead an aggressive strategy. The deck includes a variety of mana ramp creatures like Birds of Paradise and Llanowar Elves to quickly generate resources. It also utilizes cards like Giver of Runes and Mother of Runes to protect key threats. The deck can quickly tutor for important pieces with cards like Eladamri's Call and Worldly Tutor. With access to powerful removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Skyclave Apparition, the deck aims to disrupt the opponent's game plan while building up a board presence. Overall, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and efficient removal spells to secure victory."
